4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for beginners aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. Over 16 weeks, students will gain a foundation in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside practical skills in cloud security and penetration testing. The program includes three live online classes per week, with class sizes limited to 16 participants. Students receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate and can choose between English and Spanish for course content. Notably, no prior experience is required. 

For more information, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. 

